                      / Flask-blog /

                 a minimal blog application
                 inspired by Flaskr


    ~ What is Flask-blog?

      A sqlite powered thumble blog application

    ~ How do I use it?

      1. edit the configuration in the flask_blog.py file or
         export an FLASKR_SETTINGS environment variable
         pointing to a configuration file.

      2. now you can run the flask_blog.py file with your
         python interpreter and the application will
         greet you on http://localhost:5000/
	
    ~ Is it tested?

      You betcha.  Run the `test_flask_blog.py` file to see
      the tests pass.
